headline: Want $1 Million in Retirement? 3 Stocks to Buy Now and Hold for Decades.
summary: Amazon (NASDAQ: AMZN) CEO Andy Jassy often predicts in his company's quarterly conference calls what he thinks will happen with the cloud market.  Jassy will first note that at least 85% of global IT spending is still on-premises with the rest in the cloud.  Interestingly, Jassy had a similar forecast in Amazon's latest quarterly call.
